						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "[~michael], I just tested it out. I'm able to reproduce this issue on an Android 7.1 Pixel XL with right-aligned TextFields, but not left-aligned or center-aligned TextFields. Also, I'm NOT able to reproduce this issue with right-aligned TextFields on an Android 5.0 Moto G or Android 4.1 Galaxy Nexus. Hmm... this requires further investigation.\r\n\r\n[~michael], would you mind writing this up as a separate bug report please? Thanks.",
